umatoid arthritis to hit.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.041204,0.051136,0.065598,0.081546,0.094938,0.10418,0.11094,0.10919,0.10941,0.11022,0.080084,0.041563],"unified_progress":[0.043799,0.063069,0.080348,0.091118,0.097745,0.10842,0.10092,0.098916,0.093716,0.08699,0.072696,0.062259]},{"section":10,"text":"And it's not just her hands; her feet, elbows, and ankles are also affected.","dimension":6,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.060905,0.069632,0.074396,0.082754,0.089308,0.093513,0.096415,0.096102,0.096854,0.09782,0.086026,0.056275],"unified_progress":[0.054324,0.076193,0.082383,0.08734,0.093065,0.095674,0.094029,0.095882,0.09375,0.088242,0.076896,0.062222]},{"section":11,"text":"This kind of widespread joint involvement is typical for RA too.","dimension":0,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.039512,0.0851,0.094335,0.099017,0.099111,0.098286,0.095202,0.087561,0.087325,0.083109,0.076454,0.054987],"unified_progress":[0.041835,0.075042,0.089428,0.095119,0.10164,0.098903,0.099205,0.092379,0.088561,0.082034,0.075071,0.060782]},{"section":12,"text":"Oh, and there's an autoantibody found in her blood.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.027761,0.063823,0.090074,0.112,0.11943,0.11778,0.10971,0.09741,0.086672,0.079788,0.060786,0.034766],"unified_progress":[0.037489,0.071132,0.086939,0.099481,0.10395,0.1018,0.099115,0.094942,0.095624,0.083429,0.070062,0.056034]},{"section":13,"text":"It's against IgG.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.031316,0.05923,0.081131,0.10107,0.11113,0.11324,0.11058,0.10084,0.093294,0.087408,0.068042,0.042719],"unified_progress":[0.037188,0.066127,0.084214,0.09686,0.10126,0.10621,0.10111,0.096016,0.093821,0.083507,0.071795,0.061886]},{"section":14,"text":"Wait a minute, isn't that the rheumatoid factor?","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.027324,0.056022,0.07468,0.091193,0.10185,0.10858,0